# On-Schedule
Creating API for the On-Schedule online Scheduling system


# Group Groups
The user groups that share a same schedule

## Groups [/Groups]

### List all groups [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [{
          "uid": 1, 
          "description": "Let's finish this project!", 
          "isPrivate" : false,
          "creator" : "Ivan Petrov",
          "participants" : [
                {"name" :  "Anna Nikolova", "canModerate" : false},
                {"name" :  "Angel Bozhinov", "canModerate" : true},
                {"name" :  "Anelia Ninova", "canModerate" : false}
            ]
        }, {
          "uid": 2, 
          "description": "Learning English part II", 
          "isPrivate" : false,
          "creator" : "Ivaylo Zlatanov",
          "participants" : [
